-- Nissan Has Received 20,000 Orders for Leaf Electric Vehicle, Ghosn Says
-- Makiko Kitamura
-- 2010-06-23T01:39:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/nissan-has-received-20-000-orders-for-leaf-electric-vehicle-ghosn-says.html

          
          
             Nissan Motor Co. Chief Executive
Officer Carlos Ghosn said the automaker has received more than 
20,000 orders for its Leaf electric car globally. Ghosn was 
speaking at the company’s annual shareholders’ meeting.  
